{"tha-ap170:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap170:0.2":"Suparicariyavagga ","tha-ap170:0.3":"Dussadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap170:1.1":"“Tivarayam pure ramme, ","tha-ap170:1.2":"rajaputtosaham tada; ","tha-ap170:1.3":"Pannakaram labhitvana, ","tha-ap170:1.4":"upasantassadasaham. ","tha-ap170:2.1":"Adhivasesi bhagava, ","tha-ap170:2.2":"vattham hatthena amasi; ","tha-ap170:2.3":"Siddhattho adhivasetva, ","tha-ap170:2.4":"vehasam nabhamuggami. ","tha-ap170:3.1":"Buddhassa gacchamanassa, ","tha-ap170:3.2":"dussa dhavanti pacchato; ","tha-ap170:3.3":"Tattha cittam pasadesim, ","tha-ap170:3.4":"buddho no aggapuggalo. ","tha-ap170:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap170:4.2":"yam dussamadadim tada; ","tha-ap170:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap170:4.4":"dussadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap170:5.1":"Sattasatthimhito kappe, ","tha-ap170:5.2":"cakkavatti tada ahum; ","tha-ap170:5.3":"Parisuddhoti namena, ","tha-ap170:5.4":"manujindo mahabbalo. ","tha-ap170:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap170:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap170:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap170:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dussadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap170:8.1":"Dussadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}